    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as-is. While it remains functional and starts reliably, it shows significant signs of its age and mileage, including several noticeable scratches and minor dents on the exterior. The interior has some upholstery wear and the air conditioning is currently blowing weak, so the car would benefit from a mechanical tune-up and some cosmetic attention to bring it back to its best.",
